wikibase-client-data-bridge-blocked-on-c: Wo din anaa wakyiri kwan a wodedi dwuma wɔ wiki so no yɛatua no kwan.

Wakyiri kwan a yɛasi no $1 na ɔyɛeɛ. Botaeɛ ne sɛ $2.

  • Hyɛ akwansie ase: $8
  • Fa akwansie no bra awieɛ: $6

Deɛn na mɛtumi ayɛ?

Wobɛtumi ne $4 adi nkitaho anaa ɔfoƒorɔ [[{{int:grouppage-sysop}}|administrator]] de aka akwansie ho asɛm. Wobɛtumi de"{{int:emailuser}}" ahosuo adi dwuma Sɛ wode email akyiri kwan a ɛyɛ papa gya wɔ [[Special:Preferences|preferences]] so na sɛ yɛnsi wo kwan sɛ wode bɛdi dwuma a. Akwansideɛ ahyɛnsodeɛ ne #$5. Yɛsrɛ wo fa nnoɔma a ɛwɔ soro no nyinaa bra asɛmisa biara wo bisaeɛ no mu.
